Posts.Content: StephCee wrote: Please pass on info. to any youngish woman who lives in or around the St. Louis area and might be interested.  May 15 there will be a day long symposium dedicated to young women living with metastatic cancer.  Contact Jen Ivanovich to register or get more information:  314-454-5076 Log in to post a reply
